    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of hardy herbaceous, annual plant having flower heads with blue, pink, or white rays. It is native to the Mediterranean region and widely cultivated in North America. It is a common garden plant and also appears as a weed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
